      "subtasks": [],
      "created": "2013-11-08T09:27:17.332+0000",
      "description": "YARN-914 proposes graceful decommission of an NM, and NMs already have the right to go offline.\n\nIf AMs could be told that a container completed from an NM option -offline vs decommission, the AM could use that in its future blacklisting and placement policy. \n\nThis matters in long-lived services which may like to place new instances where they were placed before, and track hosts failure rates",
      "priority": {
